oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Bobby Fulcher and Lenny Johnson at the Tennessee Folklore Society's 50th anniversary
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Folklorist and TN State park ranger Bobby Fulcher and ballad singer Lenny Johnson cut the cake at the 50th anniversary celebration of the Tennessee Folklore Society.
Images were taken Oct. 19 and 20 at the 50th anniversary celebration of the Tennessee Folklore Society that took place in Cookeville, TN.
